{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "14", "m": "07", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "01", "M": "17", "S": "57"}}, "news": [{"title": "NGT halts all constructions inside Ghaziabad city forest", "para": "The National Green Tribunal has ordered the Ghaziabad district magistrate to stop illegal construction. This directive came after a plea alleged damage to Sai Upwan city forest. The tribunal noted that arguments from the applicant remained uncontroverted. Sai Upwan is a notified city forest under Ghaziabad Master Plans. The next hearing for this significant environmental matter is scheduled for September 16.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/regulatory/ngt-prohibits-illegal-constructions-in-ghaziabads-sai-upwan-city-forest/132369366?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-1232827/132369366.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "regulatory"}, {"title": "UP-RERA issues guidelines for refund of excess GST collected from homebuyers", "para": "UP-RERA has clarified the procedure for refund of excess GST collected from allottees in registered real estate projects. It has directed promoters to collect GST only at rates notified by the government.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/rera/up-rera-implements-refund-guidelines-for-excess-gst-charged-to-homebuyers/132367215?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-43148/132367215.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "rera"}, {"title": "Smartworks leases over 930 seats to professional services firm in Pune", "para": "Smartworks has leased over 930 seats in Pune to the Indian subsidiary of a UK-headquartered professional services and technology firm. The 60-month engagement is expected to generate rental revenue of about \u20b958 crore.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/commercial/smartw